member.name: F:Leadtools.Barcode.BarcodeAlignment.Center
member.summary: Aligns the barcode to the center BarcodeData.Bounds. This is horizontal center (LeadRect.Left + (LeadRect.Width - "barcodeWidth") / 2) when this is a horizontal alignment or the vertical center (LeadRect.Top + (LeadRect.Height - "barcodeHeight") / 2) when this is a vertical alignment.

member.name: F:Leadtools.Barcode.BarcodeAlignment.Far
member.summary: Aligns the barcode to the far edge of BarcodeData.Bounds. This is the left edge (LeadRect.Right - "barcodeWidth") if this is a horizontal alignment or the top edge (LeadRect.Bottom - "barcodeHeight") if this is a vertical alignment.
